    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Generated from:  MR::Dirty

Marks dirty buffers that need to be uploaded to OpenGL.
Dirty flags must be moved together with renderObj_,
but not copied since renderObj_ is not copied as well
</verbatim> </para>
